==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Asquint
<hw>A*squint"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Askant</er>, <er>Squint</er>.]</ety> <def>With the eye directed to
one side; not in the straight line of vision; obliquely; awry, so as to
see distortedly; <as>as, to look <ex>asquint</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

